title: 脚步格式怎么写

replies.author: Doby_
replies.txt_content: 先输入/sbinteract create [@group:new1][@bypass /pokegive <player> Charmander]然后再输入/sbinteract add [@bypass /manuadd <player> new2]

replies.author: Arobcher
replies.txt_content:
正确的指令应该是这样的吧
/sbwalk create @bypass /manuadd  <player> 权限

sbwalk 是指走过
sbinteract 是点击
